#Describe the Dataset There are 6083 rows and 14 columns in this dataset, representing information on avocados in different regions for every week from 1/4/2015-3/25/18. This information includes average prices, number of different sizes of avocados sold, and number of different types of bags sold. The data were collected in 2018 through retailers’ cash registers based on sales of Hass avocados.
